          ],
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "ryQR2",
              "width": 380,
              "layout": "vertical",
              "gap": 18,
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "gKCAd",
                  "fill": "#053204ff",
                  "content": "01 / ABOUT",
                  "fontFamily": "Roboto Mono",
                  "fontSize": 13,
                  "fontWeight": "500",
                  "letterSpacing": 2
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "c0f66g",
                  "fill": "#053204ff",
                  "content": "Hi — I'm Pedro.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.05,
                  "fontFamily": "Poppins",
                  "fontSize": 48,
                  "fontWeight": "700",
                  "letterSpacing": -1.2
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "J69qEq",
                  "width": 64,
                  "height": 3,
                  "fill": "#39e19eff",
                  "cornerRadius": 9999
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "V4htHk",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "layout": "vertical",
              "gap": 22,
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "D7KVc",
                  "fill": "#053204ff",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "I help engineers and operators ship modern Voice AI — without drowning in the legacy stack.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.25,
                  "fontFamily": "Poppins",
                  "fontSize": 30,
                  "fontWeight": "600",
                  "letterSpacing": -0.5
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "sw9Kd",
                  "fill": "#3a4a3a",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "For 15 years I've worked at the edge of communications infrastructure — SIP, RTP, media servers, and now Voice AI. I built Routr because the open-source telephony stack needed something easier to operate. I'm now building Fonoster to make programmable voice approachable for the next million developers.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.55,
                  "fontFamily": "Poppins",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "fontWeight": "500"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "wgH64",
                  "fill": "#3a4a3a",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "Most companies don't need an entire PBX to ship a great voice experience. They need clarity. They need patterns that work. They need someone who's been on the other end of a 3 AM Asterisk crash and lived to tell about it.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.55,
                  "fontFamily": "Poppins",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "fontWeight": "500"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
